            <title>[CASSANDRA-10939] Add missing jvm options to cassandra-env.ps1</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-10939</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following dynamic JVM options are missing from cassandra-env.ps1: &lt;tt&gt;-XX:HeapDumpPath&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;-XX:CompileCommandFile&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
